<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我今天<delay8 />為<tag a="110" b="4" /><delay20 />
準備了非常棒的禮物喔，<delay frames="40" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你願意收下嗎？</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我有件事想拜託你呢！<10_4 />
希望你願意收下<delay20 />
這<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />喔。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<tag a="110" b="4" />！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我聽說你在找
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay20 />
所以我看到就直接先把它買下來了<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但仔細想想，<delay8 />你並沒有直接拜託我去買，<delay20 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我突然開始擔心，<delay20 />
萬一我搞錯了怎麼辦呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我沒有在找喔</message>
	<message label="003_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">咦？</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />唉～<delay20 />我也真是的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />居然又買了
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我完全忘記自己之前買過，
只是收起來了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就這樣放著不用也很浪費，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果<tag a="110" b="4" />不嫌棄的話，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以收下它嗎？</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這是<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你不喜歡的話，<delay8 />
要送給其他人也行喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不介意的話就用用看吧！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay8 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能幫上你的忙<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實這是以前朋友要搬家的時候，<delay20 />
我提前買起來，
打算送給他的臨別禮物喔<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過他最後<delay20 />
還是決定不搬家了呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以這東西就一直收著沒用，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你願意收下它，
真是太好了！<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />擁有再多一樣的東西，<delay8 />
不用的話也只是浪費，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我才會決定要拿出來送人喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果<tag a="110" b="4" />
願意拿去用的話，<delay8 />我會很高興的，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你願意收下真是幫了大忙呢。<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果不需要的話，<delay20 />
你愛怎麼處理都可以喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="300" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎唷！<delay20 />果然路上的傳聞是錯的呀。<delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也真是的，<delay20 />一下就被傳聞
耍得團團轉了呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，既然都已經買下來了，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個<delay8 />就送給你吧。</message>
	<message label="301" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這果然<delay8 />不是你要的東西啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過事已至此，到底是不是也沒差了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" /><delay8 />
平常總是很照顧我，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道你願不願意收下這個呢？</message>
	<message label="302" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">如果你不需要的話，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />送給其他人也沒關係喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="303" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望你能喜歡呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="400" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />突然塞東西給你，真的很抱歉！<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之後看你愛怎麼處理它，
都沒有關係喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
